didPay((address,uint256,uint256,(address.notice: Part of IJBPayDelegate, this function gets called when the project receives a payment. It will mint an NFT to the contributor (_data.beneficiary) if conditions are met.

didRedeem((address,uint256,uint256,uint2.notice: Part of IJBRedeemDelegate, this function gets called when the token holder redeems. It will burn the specified NFTs to reclaim from the treasury to the _data.beneficiary.
